Japanese: 現在所持しているロボのチェック、ＴＲＵＥ（１）が出れば所持
ソード＆シールドナイト
ワーカー・ブルドーザー

オートマン！？
２体もいるよ！
English:
Automen!?
There are two of them!

Japanese: ガロイ親方＿戦闘中真剣

信じられん。
暴走オートマンが２体……。
English:
I can't believe it.
Two Automen running rampage...

Japanese:
これまで、複数のオートマンが
同時に暴れたという
記録はない……。
English: Until now, there's never been a documented case of two Automen going berserk simultaneously..

Japanese: ガロイ親方＿戦闘中険しい

English: What in the world is going on?

Japanese: とにかく、ここは引き返すよ。
English: In any case, I'm going to reverse us out of here.

Japanese:
相手は２体。/c5最新式のマリオ
ネーションギア/c3でもなけりゃ、
勝ち目はないからね。
English:
There are two opponents. 
Without the /c5latest Marionation Gear/c3, we wouldn't stand a chance of winning.

Japanese:
大変だ！
車が襲われてる！！
English:
This is terrible!
That car is being thrashed about!!

Japanese:
以前、ここをうろついていた
オートマンだ。
English: Those Automen were prowling about here before.

Japanese:
やつら、ここを通る者を
見境なしに襲っているんだ。
English: Looks like they're just irrationally attacking anyone who passes through here.

Japanese: ガロイ親方＿戦闘中険しい

相手は２体。
厳しいが……
English:
There are two enemies.
It's doesn't look good...

Japanese: ガロイ親方＿戦闘中真剣

襲われている人を、
見捨てるわけにはいかん。
English: But, there's no way we can just abandon someone whose under attack.

Japanese:
輸送車を助けるんだ。
戦いに巻き込まないように
注意しろ。
English: Rescue that truck, and be careful not to get caught up in the crossfire.
